1) Pull down atreus firmware repo
2) Pull down the teensy_loader_cli
3) Update teensy loader make file
  * Choose mac
  * Update the sdk version
  * make
4) Drop loader into bin directory
5) Install avr dude
6) make upload
7) push the reset button.

http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/loader_mac.html
http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/loader_cli.html
https://github.com/PaulStoffregen/teensy_loader_cli
